quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  36,41,"Waayatun lahum anna hamalnathurriyyatahum fee alfulki almashhoon"
  36,42,"Wakhalaqna lahum min mithlihi mayarkaboon"
  36,43,"Wa-in nasha/ nughriqhum fala sareekhalahum wala hum yunqathoon"
  36,44,"Illa rahmatan minnawamataAAan ila heen"
  36,45,"Wa-itha qeela lahumu ittaqoo mabayna aydeekum wama khalfakum laAAallakum turhamoon"
  36,46,"Wama ta/teehim min ayatin min ayatirabbihim illa kanoo AAanha muAArideen"
  36,47,"Wa-itha qeela lahum anfiqoo mimmarazaqakumu Allahu qala allatheena kafaroolillatheena amanoo anutAAimu man law yashaoAllahu atAAamahu in antum illa fee dalalinmubeen"
  36,48,"Wayaqooloona mata hathaalwaAAdu in kuntum sadiqeen"
  36,49,"Ma yanthuroona illasayhatan wahidatan ta/khuthuhum wahumyakhissimoon"
  36,50,"Fala yastateeAAoona tawsiyatanwala ila ahlihim yarjiAAoon"
  36,51,"Wanufikha fee assoori fa-ithahum mina al-ajdathi ila rabbihim yansiloon"
  36,52,"Qaloo ya waylana manbaAAathana min marqadina hatha mawaAAada arrahmanu wasadaqaalmursaloon"
  36,53,"In kanat illa sayhatanwahidatan fa-itha hum jameeAAun ladayna muhdaroon"
  36,54,"Falyawma la tuthlamunafsun shay-an wala tujzawna illa ma kuntumtaAAmaloon"
